phpMyVisites
============

Presentation
------------
phpMyVisites is a free and powerful open source (GNU/GPL) application
for websites statistics/analytics.

Installation
------------
Upload the directory on your webserver. Chmod 777 the root directory (phpmv2/)
Go to http://www.your_site_url.com/your_phpmyvisites_directory/
And follow installation instructions.
You must have created a database before (or use an existed database).

Update
------
Upload the new phpMyVisites directory on your webserver. Go to 
http://www.your_site_url.com/your_phpmyvisites_directory/
And follow updates instructions

